🚀 Rupee Guru – AI-Powered Personal Finance Mentor

Rupee Guru is an AI-powered personal finance mentor designed to simplify financial planning and make smart money decisions accessible to everyone. It helps users analyze their financial health, plan for early retirement, and receive real-time guidance using advanced AI.
_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

💡 Features
💯 Money Health Score
Analyzes income, expenses, savings, and debt
Provides a score out of 100
Gives insights and actionable recommendations
📊 FIRE (Financial Independence) Planner
Calculates retirement corpus
Suggests monthly SIP investments
Provides asset allocation and long-term strategy
Visualizes growth using charts
🤖 AI Chat Mentor
Answers financial questions in real-time
Provides simple, practical advice
Focused on Indian financial context (SIP, PPF, NPS, etc.)
_______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

How It Works
User Input → React Frontend → Express Backend → Gemini AI → Response → UI Display
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

⚙️ Tech Stack
Frontend: React (Vite), Tailwind CSS
Backend: Node.js (Express)
AI Integration: Google Gemini API
Charts: Recharts
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
🛠 Installation & Setup
1. Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/RUPEE-GURU.git
cd RUPEE-GURU
2. Install dependencies
npm install
3. Add environment variables

Create a .env file:

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_api_key_here
4. Run the app
npm run dev
